Punjab
Dec 15, 2014
Child Sexual Abuse, Molestation
Description:
			A 16-year-old girl was allegedly molested by a youth of Sosan village in the district when she was on her way to a school, police said today.

Police has booked Balkaran Singh (23) for allegedly molesting the girl. However, the alleged accused is absconding.

The victim, in her complaint to police yesterday, had alleged the accused used to harass on her way to school. 

